# SEO-FOCUSED DEVELOPMENT RULES

## Page Development Requirements
Every page.tsx file must include:
- Dynamic metadata generation with target keywords
- Structured data schema markup (JSON-LD)
- Canonical URL specification
- Open Graph and Twitter Card optimization
- Mobile-first responsive implementation

## Content Optimization
- Primary keyword in H1, meta title, and first paragraph
- Secondary keywords in H2 headings naturally integrated
- LSI keywords distributed throughout content
- Internal linking with descriptive anchor text
- FAQ sections for long-tail keyword capture

## Component SEO Standards
SEO components must include:
- TypeScript interfaces for all props
- Comprehensive JSDoc documentation
- Error handling for missing data
- Default values for optional SEO fields
- Testing coverage for critical SEO functionality

## Target Keywords Integration
Primary targets for Vommuli Ventures:
- "Series A funding" (2,400/month) - Homepage, main service page
- "startup fundraising guide" (2,400/month) - Blog content hub
- "investment readiness" (300/month) - Assessment tools page
- "pitch deck template" (4,500/month) - Resources section

## Performance SEO
- Implement lazy loading for non-critical content
- Optimize images with WebP format and proper sizing
- Minimize layout shift with reserved space
- Use preloading for critical resources
- Implement proper caching strategies